        <p>The Xbox Series S is a compact and powerful gaming console released by Microsoft. It offers next-generation gaming experiences at an affordable price point.</p>

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1440p gaming resolution</li>
            <li>High frame rates up to 120fps</li>
            <li>Quick load times with SSD</li>
            <li>Backward compatibility with thousands of games</li>
            <li>Xbox Game Pass subscription service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Review</h2>
        <p>The Xbox Series S delivers impressive performance for its size and price. It provides smooth gameplay with excellent graphics and fast loading times. The Xbox Game Pass subscription offers a vast library of games, making it a great value for gamers.</p>
